    "body" : "<p>You could also set your conditions without AssertJ and then just verify the boolean value with AssertJ.</p>\n<p>Like this:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>boolean result = list.stream()\n                   .anyMatch(element -&gt; element.matches(regex) || element.equals(specificString));\n\nassertThat(result).isTrue()\n</code></pre>\n"
